Page: hub.docker.com


-Is a template for create an environment
-It contains all elements needed by your app (libs, env, config files, software, code, etc)
-It can have a version or snapshots based on time
-Its immutable(not modified), but it can be cloned or shared
-These images are create using a dockerfile

-Ver las imagenes instaladas
docker images
REPOSITORY	TAG	IMAGE_ID	CREATED		SIZE
hello-world	latest	bf756b1ae65	4 months ago	12.3kb
name repository	version	id				
TAG: Puedes instalar una image especificas.

-Para buscar imagenes si no quieres usar la pagina web
docker search imagenBuscar
ex: docker search ubuntu

-instalar ubuntu. se crea como un contenedor
docker pull ubuntu

-Correr ubuntu
docker run ubuntu
-Correr hello world usando ubuntu
docker run ubuntu echo 'hello world'
-Ejecutar bash de manera interactiva "-it"
docker run -it ubuntu bash


-Ver los procesos de tus images
docker ps
